{"tid":2170301,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高追壹傳媒的日子，第十三天，晴","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T01:44:04.000Z","uid":6489,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c0c8b88d8e013f6c2530e130a6b2083a382d21","tid":2170301,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"以前一看到富途壹傳媒的重倉，我就會笑自己，覺得很可悲。但是到現在，我終於明白，我並不是一個人高追了。<br />\n<br />\n今天是這十三天以來比較開心的一天，休巿的日子一定會重拾歡笑。當我平靜下來，讓我可以專心工作，但現在看不到股票變紅，我反而很討厭這感覺。以前我很有自信，決定了就會勇往直前，但是這次面對壹傳媒，我完全不知道怎麼做，我很想走前一步去彌補我的過失，但是原來這樣反而我會損失更多。當我再打開富途，眼淚好像失控似的流出來的時候，我的心好痛，我應該怎麼做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d054c0cacdf89c625b214f3626c70559cd050d8","tid":2170301,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259a15801d2b2a196eda1f976697c9462eb20135","tid":2170301,"uid":256678,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"用支牛 真係想贈你一句抵撚死"},{"pid":"71e6ff42e7780782f123d4ed83914433c4877c00","tid":2170301,"uid":33032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"放手 放開所有 彼此更自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70844ef8012a594195e0120af0a32b3e952ebb2e","tid":2170301,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"259a15801d2b2a196eda1f976697c9462eb20135","tid":2170301,"uid":256678,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"用支牛 真係想贈你一句抵撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"可以用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336608e19736baa465e816d785a4bf1dcb8bebb2","tid":2170301,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":